# Keep the Vercel deployment lean: exclude the Python project tooling and tests
# that the static site (public/) and serverless function (api/analyze.py) don't
# need. The bet_assistant package IS kept — the function imports it, and Vercel's
# Python builder bundles imported local modules automatically (zero-config).
pyproject.toml
tests/
scripts/
.github/
.gitignore
*.md
**/__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
